      <title>安联希望将四分之三的利润重新分配给股东</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/allianz-wants-redistribute-three-quarters-profit-shareholders-2024-12-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国安联保险公司周一表示，计划在未来三年内将至少四分之三的净利润通过股息和股票回购的方式分配给股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/allianz-wants-redistribute-three-quarters-profit-shareholders-2024-12-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 20:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
