      <title>欧元区 12 月投资者信心跌至一年多以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-investor-morale-falls-december-lowest-more-than-year-2024-12-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一公布的一项调查显示，欧元区 12 月份投资者信心跌至一年多以来的最低点，德国仍然是欧元区的拖累因素，因为 2 月份的提前选举未能激发投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/euro-zone-investor-morale-falls-december-lowest-more-than-year-2024-12-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 09:33:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
